lead_paragraph: Mexican Formula One driver Esteban Gutierrez, who has yet to score a point for the Haas Formula One team in 18 races, indicated on Thursday that he could be on the way out.

headline.print_headline: Gutierrez Considering Leaving Haas F1 Team
